Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Reagan declares candidacy
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z97q3
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 23 Nov 1975
Former California governor Ronald Reagan declares he wants Republican candidacy for next presidential election. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less